data.description: FHA Buyers, Now is your time to get in! Discover this beautifully upgraded 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath home with a newly added 1-bedroom, 1-bath attached ADU. At its heart lies a contemporary kitchen adorned with white granite countertops, a vast island, and sleek grey, soft-close cabinets. Savor the fresh aesthetics of new laminate flooring, updated windows, and a new sliding backdoor. Enhancements like a renovated laundry space, energy-efficient A/C, heating, and an upgraded electrical panel ensure optimal comfort. Upstairs, the renovation continues with fresh laminate in the middle bedroom and newly installed cozy carpet in all of the other bedrooms. Adjacent to the main dwelling is a luxurious Junior ADU. This beautiful extension showcases a tasteful kitchenette, complete with white granite, soft close cabinets, a spacious walk-in closet, and a beautifully designed bathroom equipped with an elegant shower and an acrylic flat-bottom tub. Its own tankless water heater and dedicated mini-split A/C further enhance its appeal. The outdoor space has been thoughtfully redesigned with new pavers, a contemporary privacy fence and the addition of an electric remote-access gate that offers secure parking options that can fit up to 6 additional cars or work trucks. Notably, the roof, replaced in 2016, stands as a testament to the home's recent upgrades. A cutting-edge security system ensures safety and provides an added sense of security. Positioned for convenience, this residence provides quick access to freeways, public transportation, downtown LA, and Sofi Stadium. With major upgrades complete, this home awaits your personal touch. Don't miss this chance to make it yours.
